                            <comment id="17063458" author="lne3" created="Fri, 20 Mar 2020 15:36:22 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Most likely this issue is due to removal of deprecated org.testng.TestNG.addListener(Lorg/testng/ITestListener; ) in &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/cbeust/testng/commit/b187d08067d16f4e1cf162e90ca12f95bbd39dfb#diff-c89ea27c996c668601a33f887b5675f2&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/cbeust/testng/commit/b187d08067d16f4e1cf162e90ca12f95bbd39dfb#diff-c89ea27c996c668601a33f887b5675f2&lt;/a&gt; .&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17064222" author="tibor17" created="Sun, 22 Mar 2020 10:10:39 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=juherr&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;juherr&quot;&gt;juherr&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
Hi Julien,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We are still using the deprecated method &quot;addListener&quot;.&lt;br/&gt;
Can you pls show us what other method we can use instead?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Thx&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17064411" author="lne3" created="Sun, 22 Mar 2020 20:42:05 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Hello &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=tibordigana&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;tibordigana&quot;&gt;tibordigana&lt;/a&gt;,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;please find a possible solution at &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/maven-surefire/pull/276&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/maven-surefire/pull/276&lt;/a&gt; .&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;There are still addListener methods, but the one that takes a ITestListener has been removed. The patch uses the same approach as addListener a few lines above at &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/maven-surefire/blob/8ae235f8f9099f6f07f7fc23d3c0e971448a7192/surefire-providers/surefire-testng/src/main/java/org/apache/maven/surefire/testng/TestNGExecutor.java#L305&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;line 305&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Thank you&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17064440" author="tibor17" created="Sun, 22 Mar 2020 22:49:41 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://gitbox.apache.org/repos/asf?p=maven-surefire.git;a=commit;h=5534bd7590af1e3ff8b7706e788a1c2214e70141&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://gitbox.apache.org/repos/asf?p=maven-surefire.git;a=commit;h=5534bd7590af1e3ff8b7706e788a1c2214e70141&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17064589" author="juherr" created="Mon, 23 Mar 2020 07:24:57 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I&apos;m a bit too late but as pointed on &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/maven-surefire/pull/276#issuecomment-602426682&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;Github&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;tt&gt;addListener(ITestNGListener)&lt;/tt&gt; is a better choice (if possible) because &lt;tt&gt;addListener(Object)&lt;/tt&gt; is deprecated and will be removed a day.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17065131" author="lne3" created="Mon, 23 Mar 2020 21:54:37 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;2nd attempt: &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/maven-surefire/pull/278&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/maven-surefire/pull/278&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Additionally, it changes further &lt;tt&gt;addListener(Object)&lt;/tt&gt; calls to &lt;tt&gt;addListener(ITestNGListener).&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17065496" author="tibor17" created="Tue, 24 Mar 2020 10:30:30 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://gitbox.apache.org/repos/asf?p=maven-surefire.git;a=commit;h=e23253e555e8c9844abd99e2d51968386c9ead24&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://gitbox.apache.org/repos/asf?p=maven-surefire.git;a=commit;h=e23253e555e8c9844abd99e2d51968386c9ead24&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17685262" author="nahguam" created="Tue, 7 Feb 2023 12:11:57 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This appears to still be an issue as &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/maven-surefire/blob/master/surefire-providers/surefire-testng-utils/src/main/java/org/apache/maven/surefire/testng/utils/FailFastListener.java#L33&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;FailFastListener&lt;/a&gt; still implements ITestListener and is called in &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/maven-surefire/blob/master/surefire-providers/surefire-testng/src/main/java/org/apache/maven/surefire/testng/TestNGExecutor.java#L350-L351&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;TestNGExecutor&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17995155" author="olamy" created="Fri, 4 Jul 2025 07:35:28 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This project has moved from Jira to GitHub Issues. This issue was migrated to &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/maven-surefire/issues/3092&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;apache/maven-surefire#3092&lt;/a&gt;. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
